          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/1746.-step-4-x1500.jpg",
            "width": 1500
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Drain and rinse the <strong>butter beans </strong></p>\n<p>Dissolve the <strong>soft cheese</strong> in 50ml<span class=\"text-danger\"> [100ml]</span> <strong>boiled water</strong> – this is your <strong>creamy stock</strong></p>",
      "order": 5,
      "media": {
        "images": [
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/1746.-step-5-x200.jpg",
            "width": 200
          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/1746.-step-5-x400.jpg",
            "width": 400
          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/1746.-step-5-x700.jpg",
            "width": 700
          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/1746.-step-5-x1000.jpg",
            "width": 1000
          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/1746.-step-5-x1500.jpg",
            "width": 1500
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Heat a separate large, wide-based pan (preferably non-stick) with a drizzle of <strong>olive oil </strong>over a medium heat</p>\n<p>Once hot, add the <strong>drained butter beans </strong>to the pan with the <strong>chopped spring onion</strong> and <strong>garlic</strong> and cook for 1 min</p>\n<p>Add the <strong>creamy stock</strong>, season with a generous pinch of <strong>salt</strong> and <strong>pepper</strong> and cook for 3-4 min or until thickened<span class=\"text-highlight\"> – these are your <strong>creamy butter beans</strong></span> </p>",
      "order": 6,
      "media": {
        "images": [
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/1746.-step-6-x200.jpg",
            "width": 200
          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/1746.-step-6-x400.jpg",
            "width": 400
          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/1746.-step-6-x700.jpg",
            "width": 700
          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/1746.-step-6-x1000.jpg",
            "width": 1000
          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/1746.-step-6-x1500.jpg",
            "width": 1500
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Add a splash of<strong> boiled water</strong> to the reserved steak pan and scrape the bottom of the pan with a wooden spoon</p>\n<p>Pour the <strong>pan</strong> <strong>juices</strong> into the<strong> creamy butter beans </strong></p>\n<p>Combine 2 tbsp <span class=\"text-danger\">[4 tbsp]</span> <strong>olive oil</strong> with the <strong>balsamic vinegar</strong> in a bowl – this is your <strong>dressing</strong></p>",
      "order": 7,
      "media": {
        "images": [
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/1746.-step-7-x200.jpg",
            "width": 200
          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/1746.-step-7-x400.jpg",
            "width": 400
          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/1746.-step-7-x700.jpg",
            "width": 700
          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/1746.-step-7-x1000.jpg",
            "width": 1000
          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/1746.-step-7-x1500.jpg",
            "width": 1500
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Serve the <strong>rested steak</strong> over the <strong>creamy butter beans</strong> with a handful of <strong>rocket</strong> to the side</p>\n<p>Drizzle the <strong>dressing</strong> over the <strong>rocket</strong> and serve the <strong>warmed focaccia</strong> on the side</p>\n<p>Enjoy!</p>",
      "order": 8,
